Overview:
This repository contains data showing the "best" neighborhood in the greater Pittsburgh area by the metric of safety. Using data like arrests, income, home value, and college degrees, this repository contains the information to discover the safest, wealthiest, and most educated area to live in.

References:
Very specific and large dataset by neighborhood(income, crime, population, size, profession, etc) https://data.wprdc.org/dataset/neighborhoods-with-snap-data/resource/bce22c26-9d3e-4e3f-8405-a35c4b7765b6 
Aggregate Salary: https://data.wprdc.org/dataset/pittsburgh-american-community-survey-2015-miscellaneous-data/resource/34842307-0da6-458a-9df3-a09ab3e3a489  
Housing Market Value: https://data.wprdc.org/dataset/market-value-analysis-allegheny-county-economic-development/resource/f7a3851b-904a-4ae9-985a-86cd266c906d
Arrest Data : https://data.wprdc.org/datastore/dump/e03a89dd-134a-4ee8-a2bd-62c40aeebc6f
